Achievements.Name: Campaign Completed (Easy)
Achievements.Description: Complete campaign mode with any combination of single player and co-op on Easy difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Campaign Completed (Normal)
Achievements.Description: Complete campaign mode with any combination of single player and co-op on Normal difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Campaign Completed (Hard)
Achievements.Description: Complete campaign mode with any combination of single player and co-op on Hard difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Campaign Completed (Extreme)
Achievements.Description: Complete campaign mode with any combination of single player and co-op on Extreme difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Lang Time Dead
Achievements.Description: Complete any campaign or co-op mission with at least 50 kills and 30% accuracy using Lang.

Achievements.Name: Graves Digger
Achievements.Description: Complete any mission with at least 50 kills and 40% accuracy using Graves.

Achievements.Name: Ain't Got Time To Bleed
Achievements.Description: Complete any Campaign or Co-op mission without going MIA (no loads or checkpoint resumes allowed).

Achievements.Name: Kill Streak
Achievements.Description: Score 50 kills in a row without going MIA.

Achievements.Name: Splash Damage
Achievements.Description: Achieve 10 grenade kills in one mission.

Achievements.Name: Brawler
Achievements.Description: Achieve 10 melee kills in one single player or co-op mission.

Achievements.Name: Minute Man
Achievements.Description: Destroy 45 objects in 60 seconds.

Achievements.Name: Scorched Earth
Achievements.Description: Destroy at least 75% of destroyable objects in a mission.

Achievements.Name: Collateral Damage
Achievements.Description: Make 10 indirect kills in a mission by shooting explosive objects such as barrels or gas cylinders.

Achievements.Name: One Careful Owner
Achievements.Description: Ensure BMP survives until the end of Monastery.

Achievements.Name: Saving Private Yelkin
Achievements.Description: Ensure Private Yelkin survives in Whaling Station.

Achievements.Name: Easy Slider
Achievements.Description: Commandeer hovercraft and ensure it survives to perimeter wall in Submarine Facility.

Achievements.Name: Vertically Challenged
Achievements.Description: Destroy Jump-Jet in Submarine Facility.

Achievements.Name: Defend The Doctor
Achievements.Description: Ensure Dr. Pessich survives until end of Castle.

Achievements.Name: Compound Problem
Achievements.Description: Escape from police compound without going MIA in Township.

Achievements.Name: Police Protection
Achievements.Description: Save RPF troops in town square in Township.

Achievements.Name: Search And Rescue
Achievements.Description: Rescue Bishop Three in Township.

Achievements.Name: Your Cousin Dances Naked...
Achievements.Description: Listen in on 4 guard conversations in Diamond Mine without being detected.

Achievements.Name: Out Of Sight
Achievements.Description: Track Atongwe in Diamond Mine without being detected.

Achievements.Name: Prisoner Release Programme
Achievements.Description: Ensure FSB Agents survive until the end of Castle.

Achievements.Name: Change Of Priority
Achievements.Description: Ensure hostages survive on Tanker.

Achievements.Name: Deal Breaker
Achievements.Description: Track down and kill Kwennoir in Sawmill.

Achievements.Name: Curse Of The Bambino
Achievements.Description: Rescue Foley in Sawmill.

Achievements.Name: Delta Force Stay The Course
Achievements.Description: Ensure all Delta Force members survive until the end of Oil Refinery.

Achievements.Name: Gas Tap
Achievements.Description: Prevent gas from being released in Military Base.

Achievements.Name: Co-operative Mission
Achievements.Description: Complete any mission in Co-op.

Achievements.Name: Co-operative Campaign
Achievements.Description: Complete a full campaign in Co-op.

Achievements.Name: Perfect Partner
Achievements.Description: Complete a Co-op mission without either player going MIA.

Achievements.Name: Top Of The Pile
Achievements.Description: Finish first in a Deathmatch Ranked Match with 16 players.

Achievements.Name: Deathmatch Dominator
Achievements.Description: Win a Deathmatch Ranked match, scoring double the kills of your nearest rival.

Achievements.Name: Deathmatch Killing Streak
Achievements.Description: Score 15 consecutive kills in a Deathmatch Ranked match.

Achievements.Name: Won Deathmatch With Lang
Achievements.Description: Win a Deathmatch Ranked match playing only as Lang.

Achievements.Name: Won Deathmatch With Graves
Achievements.Description: Win a Deathmatch Ranked match playing only as Graves.

Achievements.Name: Carrying The Team
Achievements.Description: Score over 50% of a winning teams points in a Team Deathmatch Ranked Match.

Achievements.Name: Team Deathmatch Killing Streak
Achievements.Description: Score 15 consecutive kills for a single team in a Team Deathmatch Ranked Match (Any weapon).

Achievements.Name: Won Team Deathmatch With Lang
Achievements.Description: Win a Team Deathmatch Ranked match playing only as Lang.

Achievements.Name: Won Team Deathmatch With Graves
Achievements.Description: Win a Team Deathmatch Ranked match playing only as Graves.

Achievements.Name: Clean Sweep
Achievements.Description: Hold all 5 flags for at least 30 seconds in a Conquest Ranked match.

Achievements.Name: Conquest Conquerors
Achievements.Description: Score double the other teams points in a Conquest Ranked match.

Achievements.Name: Healing Hands
Achievements.Description: Heal 10 team members in a Conquest Ranked match.
